                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">猫爪护盾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/47826599/e0be64da66db784af5d4f957d93b6fad_8294895603213822498.png",
